Irene Franklin https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Irene_Franklin 0 Irene Franklin (13 June 1876 in New York City, New York – 16 June 1941 in Englewood, New Jersey), was an American actress of stage and screen, vaudeville comedian, and singer.
